{"tid":1645023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一定要罷工，直至還陳彥霖清白","createTime":"2019-10-10T17:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T06:31:31.000Z","uid":20559,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8625fce94afdfd71bdbfb4b6ce48b796fcd61c27","tid":1645023,"uid":20559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:54:20.000Z","msg":"我相信<br />\n<br />\n黑警係呢個時候公布彥霖身份<br />\n<br />\n絕對係有所企圖<br />\n<br />\n第一<br />\n<br />\n黑警點會唔識處理屍體而不被察覺？<br />\n<br />\n佢哋係最清楚如何殺人毀屍滅跡<br />\n<br />\n所以我堅信<br />\n<br />\n佢話你聽有死人，係因為佢想你知道<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n<br />\n點解佢想大眾知道有少女死？<br />\n<br />\n配合近呢個星期港共做法，就係要進一步激起憤怒<br />\n<br />\n佢要大家殺警，要大家燒鋪，要做到好難睇<br />\n<br />\n要國際社會，尤其係美國割蓆<br />\n<br />\n港共要孤立香港投爭者<br />\n<br />\n同時佢一定會搏命拉勇武<br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪代表乜都唔洗做<br />\n<br />\n唔係<br />\n<br />\n我哋要宣傳開去<br />\n<br />\n將彥霖嘅死訊話比身邊嘅人知，全世界知<br />\n<br />\n然後發起無限期罷工，鼓勵身邊嘅人要勇敢罷工<br />\n<br />\n罷工只有一個原因<br />\n<br />\n要求黑警清楚交代陳彥霖死因，唔能夠比佢死得不明不白<br />\n<br />\n罷工一定要人多，目標一定要清晰<br />\n<br />\n我會係公司group send以下message<br />\n<br />\n本人現參與無限期罷工，要求香港政府清楚交代陳彥霖死因。我愛香港人，每個少男都是我的弟弟，每個少女都是我的妹妹。我斷不能坐看弟妹被傷害而默不吭聲。謹此對公司帶來的麻煩致歉，還望見諒。<br />\n<br />\n最後，rest in peace"},{"pid":"c0aad60d16c447bab69243b39d5388a0dd29e07c","tid":1645023,"uid":35104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9385fc4247bd189056d0a4f53f21021c41851a","tid":1645023,"uid":20559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:55:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n我信香港人夠膽做<br />\n為香港而做<br />\n無限期罷工！"},{"pid":"90c209d484eeae9c15f484be69d4fa4bff5338ac","tid":1645023,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:56:02.000Z","msg":"美國已經好難割蓆"},{"pid":"dd29dfeb0e42b0e42f77f8cdee9121d7ea820615","tid":1645023,"uid":187812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:56:51.000Z","msg":"跨界別抗爭籌備組： 致香港人的信&lt;You May Say I&rsquo;m a DREAMER&gt;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1643981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1643981</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mGt3CAc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmGt3CAc.jpg&h=daa34770&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v87G8GU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv87G8GU.jpg&h=59baf02e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b28bc5198e27dc0a1f6be6f52610731e85f5caf","tid":1645023,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:58:06.000Z","msg":"10月6日至10月7日 以下句子一直蔓延 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">&quot;<strong>等美國通過法案啦 忍下手啦 唔差在呢幾日啦, 我地比律師朋友做野啦 休息啦..............&quot;</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">結果呢? 呢幾日發生咩事啊?</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">看更因為拒絕比暴徒進入住所被捕<br />\n暴徒街上亂咁拉 有無口罩都拉<br />\n黨鐵日日宵禁 屈示威者<br />\n浮屍又出現 未成年既都有</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n你班休息撚係咪又想<span style=\"color: red;\">等等等</span>?<br />\n等到<span style=\"color: red;\">新彊嶺建成全港200萬人一齊送入去集中營先行動好無?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪再信咩野仲有幾多日通法案忍下手<br />\n咩野律師朋友做緊野忍下手<br />\n咩野民意逆轉外媒唔鐘意暴力忍下手<br />\n...........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢場不是不合作運動, 呢場不是公民抗命咁簡單<br />\n呢場係一場革命, 係一場戰爭, 雙方都將所有賭本儘押<br />\n根本係無任何空間可以喘息 你估暴徒一方就算無活動, 又唔係晚晚開OT搜證拉人咩?<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地會休息咩?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估林鄭開行會無傾過動用更多緊急法咩?<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地會休息咩?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地<span style=\"color: red;\">只要人,<strong>一齊趕絕休息撚 付諸行動 自己香港要自己救<br />\n<br />\n不要將抗爭外判 不要愧對義士 不要令自己後悔</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E1ERLcz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE1ERLcz.jpg&h=1ea16afc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0186c512304216cdf40aa68a3ecc249347e2308","tid":1645023,"uid":20559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:58:31.000Z","msg":"喂大佬<br />\n<br />\n已經無辦法逃避現實<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係現實<br />\n<br />\n現實就係殘酷<br />\n<br />\n我唔想見到再多一個受害者<br />\n<br />\n一個都唔想"},{"pid":"74257eb03f8acb4486b664e42f338cc75a8009c6","tid":1645023,"uid":70458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:59:28.000Z","msg":"仲講罷工<br />\n我已經覺得而家就算有證有據黑警謀殺強姦<br />\n香港人都係繼續返工<br />\n最多上fb 鬧兩句<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083f3451075cee4317759048ac3779a9006eb235","tid":1645023,"uid":20559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:59:35.000Z","msg":"我同你講，如果不了了之，呢種事一定會再發生<br />\n<br />\n如果佢係你細妹，你會點？"},{"pid":"e95c8f33ce43086